mods.abstract:
 Text 1: ff. 1r,3-142r,12: 151 Psalms;  
Text 2: ff. 142v,1-176r,end: Canticles of the Prophets: 
The Prayer of Moses 1st, 2nd, 3rd (f. 142v,1), Prayer of Hanna, the mother of Samuel (f. 147v,8), of Hezekiah King of Judah (f. 148v,11), of Manasseh “the Prophet” (f. 149v,2), of Jonah “the Prophet” (f. 150v,9), of Daniel “the Prophet” (f. 151r,9), of the Three Youths (in the oven) (f. 152r,last), of Habbakuk (f. 153v,11), of Isaiah (f. 155v,1), of Mary (Magnificat) (f. 156v,3), of Zachariah (Benedictus) (f. 157r,2), of Simeon (Nunc dimittis) (f. 157v,6);  
Text 3: ff. 158r,1-185v,end: Song of Songs (Mäḫaləyä mäḫaləy);  
Text 4: ff. 166va,1-178rb,8: Praise of our Lady Mary (Wəddaseha lä-᾽əgzə᾽ətnä Maryam); (text in 2 columns);  
Text 5: ff. 178rb,8-183vb,end: Praise and Thanksgivings (to Mary) (Wəddase wä-gənay); (text in 2 columns);  
Text 6: ff. 184ra,1-189vb,end (not complete): a prayer: Listen, O Lord, to my prayer, Alleluya, Alleluya, …

